  <p style="font-size:15px;color:var(--cm);max-width:520px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;line-height:1.75;">CodaCo connects you with clients who are actively seeking support around death and dying — whether that's a handmade urn, an estate attorney, or a compassionate death doula. Join a curated community built with care.</p>
