  <div style="max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:2rem;"><div class="ey">Why CodaCo</div><h2 class="sh">Built for this work, by people who understand it</h2></div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:16px;">
      <div style="background:var(--wh);border-radius:10px;padding:1.4rem 1.25rem;border:1px solid rgba(44,40,37,.07);"><div style="width:36px;height:36px;margin-bottom:.9rem;"><svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="14" stroke="#C1634F" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M12 18 L16 22 L24 14" stroke="#C1634F" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ch);margin-bottom:.35rem;">Curated audience</div><div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--cl);line-height:1.6;">Every visitor is here intentionally — actively seeking goods and services related to death and dying.</div></div>
