<div class="form-layout">
<div class="form-main">
  <div class="form-section"><div class="form-sh">Step 1 — Your seller profile</div><div class="form-sh-sub">This is how buyers will know and trust you. You can edit this at any time.</div>
    <div class="fg2"><div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">First name</label><input class="fi" value="Nora"/></div><div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Last name</label><input class="fi" value="Hayashi"/></div></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Shop / business name</label><input class="fi" value="Earthen Studio"/></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Email address</label><input class="fi" type="email" value="nora@earthenstudio.com"/></div>
    <div class="fg2"><div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">City</label><input class="fi" value="Portland"/></div><div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">State</label><select class="fi"><option>OR</option><option>CA</option><option>NY</option><option>TX</option></select></div></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">About you <span>(shown on your profile)</span></label><textarea class="fi">Nora Hayashi has been throwing functional ceramics for over fifteen years. After losing her own mother, she began making urns as a way of honoring the people who shape us. Every piece is made with intention.</textarea></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Website or social link <span>(optional)</span></label><input class="fi" placeholder="https://"/></div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-section"><div class="form-sh">Step 2 — Your listing</div><div class="form-sh-sub">Describe your product clearly and warmly. You can add multiple listings after your first is approved.</div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Product name</label><input class="fi" value="Hand-thrown ceramic urn, sage glaze"/></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Category</label><select class="fi"><option>Urns &amp; vessels</option><option>Ash jewelry</option><option>Burial shrouds</option><option>Planning documents</option><option>Memorial art &amp; prints</option><option>Custom keepsakes</option><option>Gifts &amp; humor</option><option>Other</option></select></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Description</label><textarea class="fi" style="min-height:110px;">Each urn is hand-thrown on the wheel in my Portland studio. The sage glaze is fired at high temperature, producing a matte, earthy finish with subtle natural variation — no two are identical. Designed to hold the cremated remains of one adult, with a threaded lid for secure, dignified closure.</textarea></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Tags <span>(select all that apply)</span></label><div class="cp-row"><span class="cp on">Handmade</span><span class="cp on">Ceramic</span><span class="cp">Eco-friendly</span><span class="cp on">Ships anywhere</span><span class="cp">Local pickup</span><span class="cp">Custom / personalized</span><span class="cp">Made to order</span><span class="cp">Digital download</span></div></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Availability</label>
      <div class="rc-card on" onclick="selRc(this,'ship')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Ships anywhere in the US</div></div></div>
      <div class="rc-card" onclick="selRc(this,'ship')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Local pickup only</div></div></div>
      <div class="rc-card" onclick="selRc(this,'ship')" style="margin-top:-2px;"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Both — ships and local pickup</div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-section"><div class="form-sh">Step 3 — Photos &amp; pricing</div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Product photos <span>(up to 8 · first photo is your cover image)</span></label>
      <div class="upload-zone"><svg width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" style="margin:0 auto;display:block;"><rect x="4" y="8" width="24" height="18" rx="3" stroke="#9A9189" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M16 14 L16 22" stroke="#9A9189" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M12 18 L16 14 L20 18" stroke="#9A9189" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/></svg><p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--cl);margin-top:.5rem;">Click to upload or drag and drop</p><span style="font-size:12px;color:var(--cl);">JPG, PNG, WebP · max 10MB each</span></div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:.75rem;">
        <div style="width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:8px;border:1.5px solid var(--tr);background:var(--tp);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><svg width="32" height="38" viewBox="0 0 60 70" fill="none"><path d="M30 8 C18 8 10 20 10 38 C10 52 18 62 30 62 C42 62 50 52 50 38 C50 20 42 8 30 8Z" stroke="#C1634F" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/></svg></div>
        <div style="width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid rgba(44,40,37,.12);background:var(--pl2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none"><circle cx="30" cy="30" r="16" stroke="#5A534C" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none"/></svg></div>
        <div style="width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:8px;border:1.5px dashed rgba(44,40,37,.2);background:var(--pl);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><line x1="10" y1="3" x2="10" y2="17" stroke="#9A9189" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="17" y2="10" stroke="#9A9189" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Pricing <span>(add variants if you offer different sizes or options)</span></label>
      <div id="ptable">
        <div class="price-row"><input class="fi" value="Standard (200 cu in)" style="font-size:13px;"/><input class="fi" value="145" style="width:80px;font-size:13px;" placeholder="Price $"/><input class="fi" value="12" style="width:70px;font-size:13px;" placeholder="Stock"/><button class="price-del" onclick="delRow(this)">×</button></div>
        <div class="price-row"><input class="fi" value="Large (280 cu in)" style="font-size:13px;"/><input class="fi" value="185" style="width:80px;font-size:13px;"/><input class="fi" value="8" style="width:70px;font-size:13px;"/><button class="price-del" onclick="delRow(this)">×</button></div>
        <div class="price-row"><input class="fi" value="Keepsake (30 cu in)" style="font-size:13px;"/><input class="fi" value="68" style="width:80px;font-size:13px;"/><input class="fi" value="20" style="width:70px;font-size:13px;"/><button class="price-del" onclick="delRow(this)">×</button></div>
