<div class="form-main">
  <div class="form-section"><div class="form-sh">Step 1 — Your provider profile</div><div class="form-sh-sub">Clients will see this when they find your listing. Be warm and specific — this work is personal.</div>
    <div class="fg2"><div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">First name</label><input class="fi" value="Maria"/></div><div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Last name</label><input class="fi" value="Rosales"/></div></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Practice / business name <span>(optional)</span></label><input class="fi" placeholder="e.g. Threshold Wellness"/></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Credentials / certifications</label><input class="fi" value="CEND, certified end-of-life doula"/></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Email address</label><input class="fi" type="email" value="maria@rosaleseoling.com"/></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Phone <span>(shown only to confirmed inquiries)</span></label><input class="fi" placeholder="(555) 000-0000"/></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">About you <span>(your story, your approach, your values)</span></label><textarea class="fi" style="min-height:110px;">I'm a certified end-of-life doula with 8 years of experience supporting individuals and families through the dying process. I specialize in home-centered dying, advance care conversations, and vigil support. I bring calm, presence, and compassion to every engagement.</textarea></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Website or social link <span>(optional)</span></label><input class="fi" placeholder="https://"/></div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-section"><div class="form-sh">Step 2 — Your service</div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Service type</label><select class="fi"><option>Death doula</option><option>Estate attorney</option><option>Death cleaning (döstädning)</option><option>Funeral celebrant</option><option>EOL organizer</option><option>Home funeral guide</option><option>Grief counselor</option><option>Legacy / life review specialist</option><option>Other</option></select></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Service description</label><textarea class="fi" style="min-height:110px;">I offer one-on-one doula support across the arc of dying — from advance care planning and family conversations, through active dying and vigil. I work in-home and can also support clients remotely. LGBTQ+ affirming.</textarea></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Specializations <span>(select all that apply)</span></label><div class="cp-row"><span class="cp sg-pill on">EOL planning</span><span class="cp sg-pill on">Advance care directives</span><span class="cp sg-pill on">Vigil support</span><span class="cp sg-pill on">LGBTQ+ affirming</span><span class="cp sg-pill">Grief support</span><span class="cp sg-pill">Bilingual (Spanish)</span><span class="cp sg-pill">Perinatal loss</span><span class="cp sg-pill">Dementia &amp; memory care</span><span class="cp sg-pill">Cultural/religious customs</span></div></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Session format</label>
      <div class="rc-card on" onclick="selRcGroup(this,'fmt')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Both in-person and virtual</div></div></div>
      <div class="rc-card" onclick="selRcGroup(this,'fmt')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">In-person only</div></div></div>
      <div class="rc-card" onclick="selRcGroup(this,'fmt')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Virtual only</div></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Pricing model</label>
      <div class="rc-card on" onclick="selRcGroup(this,'pricemdl')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Hourly rate</div><div class="rc-desc">e.g. $120/hour</div></div></div>
      <div class="rc-card" onclick="selRcGroup(this,'pricemdl')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Package / flat rate</div><div class="rc-desc">e.g. $850 for full support package</div></div></div>
      <div class="rc-card" onclick="selRcGroup(this,'pricemdl')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Sliding scale</div><div class="rc-desc">Income-based or contact me to discuss</div></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="fg2"><div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Starting rate <span>(or range)</span></label><input class="fi" placeholder="e.g. $120/hr or $800–$1,200"/></div><div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Free consultation?</label><select class="fi"><option>Yes — 30 min free</option><option>Yes — 15 min free</option><option>No free consultation</option></select></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-section"><div class="form-sh">Step 3 — Service area &amp; availability</div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Primary location</label><div class="fg3" style="margin-bottom:0;"><input class="fi" value="Brooklyn"/><select class="fi"><option>NY</option><option>CA</option><option>TX</option></select><input class="fi" value="11201" placeholder="ZIP code"/></div></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Service radius</label><div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;"><button class="cp sg-pill">5 miles</button><button class="cp sg-pill on">15 miles</button><button class="cp sg-pill">30 miles</button><button class="cp sg-pill">50 miles</button><button class="cp sg-pill">Statewide</button><button class="cp sg-pill">National (virtual)</button></div></div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Typical availability <span>(days you generally work)</span></label>
      <div class="avail-grid"><div class="avail-day"><span>Mon</span></div><div class="avail-day on"><span>Tue</span></div><div class="avail-day on"><span>Wed</span></div><div class="avail-day on"><span>Thu</span></div><div class="avail-day on"><span>Fri</span></div><div class="avail-day"><span>Sat</span></div><div class="avail-day"><span>Sun</span></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Current availability status</label>
      <div class="rc-card on" onclick="selRcGroup(this,'avail')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Accepting new clients</div></div></div>
      <div class="rc-card" onclick="selRcGroup(this,'avail')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Waitlist only</div></div></div>
      <div class="rc-card" onclick="selRcGroup(this,'avail')"><div class="rc-dot"><div class="rc-in"></div></div><div><div class="rc-title">Not currently taking new clients</div></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="fg"><label class="fl-label">Background check &amp; credentials <span>(upload if available)</span></label>
      <div class="upload-zone" style="padding:1.25rem;text-align:left;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none"><rect x="4" y="4" width="24" height="28" rx="3" stroke="#9A9189" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><line x1="9" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12" stroke="#9A9189" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="9" y1="17" x2="23" y2="17" stroke="#9A9189" stroke-width="1.2"/><line x1="9" y1="22" x2="17" y2="22" stroke="#9A9189" stroke-width="1.2"/></svg><div><p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--cl);margin:0;">Upload certificate, license, or background check</p><span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--cl);">Documents are kept private and used for verification only.</span></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="btn-row"><button class="btn-s" onclick="go(4)">← Back</button><button class="btn-p" onclick="go(7)">Continue to plan selection →</button></div>
</div>
